text.tspan: Global meat demand if everyone ate like the average citizen of..., 1961
Hypothetical global meat demand if everyone in the world ate the same quantity as the average citizen of a given country. For
example, data for the US in 2020 shows global meat demand if everyone in the world consumed the same amount of meat as
the average US citizen in 2020. The curve for "World" gives the actual global meat production in 2020.
Data source: Food and Agriculture Organization of the United Nations (2023) and other sources
